PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773792182
OL,3,CAstronomers 'alarmed' by plans to use
OL,4,Cspace mirrors to light Earth at night
OL,6,FIt says some of the benefits could
OL,7,Finclude expanding the potential of
OL,8,Fsolar power, extending working areas,
OL,9,Freplacing streetlights, and
OL,10,Filluminating disaster zones.
OL,12,FHowever, the Royal Astronomical
OL,13,FSociety (RAS) said the satellites
OL,14,Fwould "permanently scar the natural
OL,15,Flandscape" and make the night sky
OL,16,Fthree to four times brighter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
