PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773792182
OL,3,CAstronomers 'alarmed' by plans to use
OL,4,Cspace mirrors to light Earth at night
OL,6,FDr Robert Massey, Deputy Executive
OL,7,FDirector at the RAS, said: "These
OL,8,Fproposals would not only have a
OL,9,Fdisastrous impact on the science of
OL,10,Fastronomy, they would also hinder the
OL,11,Fright of everybody on Earth to enjoy
OL,12,Fthe night sky. That is unacceptable.
OL,14,F"The stars above us are a valued part
OL,15,Fof human heritage ` deploying more
OL,16,Fthan one million exceptionally bright
OL,17,Fsatellites would utterly destroy this
OL,18,Fand permanently scar the natural
OL,19,Flandscape."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
