PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773792182
OL,3,CAstronomers 'alarmed' by plans to use
OL,4,Cspace mirrors to light Earth at night
OL,6,FAccording to Reflect Orbital's
OL,7,Fwebsite, the company plans to launch
OL,8,F50,000 satellites by 2035, with the
OL,9,Ffirst two expected to be launched by
OL,10,Fthe end of the year.
OL,12,FIt also states that they will
OL,13,F"maintain strict exclusion zones for
OL,14,Fastronomy and sensitive environments."
OL,16,FAlongside the European Southern
OL,17,FObservatory and the International
OL,18,FAstronomical Union, the RAS says they
OL,19,Fhave submitted comments opposing the
OL,20,Fplans to the US Federal Communications
OL,21,FCommission (FCC).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
